summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 76E & 77W, page 180 & 181, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Highland Park, South 60 ft. of Lot 9, Block 1, Lots 1, 4, 5 and 8, Block 8, Southwest Seattle Addition, Lots 16 and 17, Block 1, Lots 20 to 30 incl., Block 8, located on both side of 16th Ave. S.W. from line north of W. Henderson St. (1 lot north on east side - 2 lots north on west side) to line north of W. Barton St. (1 lot no. on east side - 4 lots no. on west side) as Neighborhood Business (BN) Zone.
